    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been such a reliable companion for me! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so it\u2019s totally ready for all your upcoming road trips or daily commutes. It looks great and drives even better\u2014definitely a solid find for anyone looking for a dependable ride. Feel free to reach out with any questions; I\u2019d love for you to come by and see it for yourself!",
